    "What are the problems and what are your suggestions to improve each element of the essay?",
    "Your feedback must be between 250 and 350 words).",
    "To be able to engage students in the online peer feedback activity, we used the FeedbackFruits app embedded in the Brightspace platform.",
    "FeedbackFruits functions as an external educational technology tool seamlessly integrated into Brightspace, aimed at enhancing student engagement via diverse peer collaboration approaches.",
    "Among its features are peer feedback, assignment evaluation, skill assessment, automated feedback, interactive videos, dynamic documents, discussion tasks, and engaging presentations (Noroozi et al., 2022)."
